==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: acrylonitrile
<hw>acrylonitrile</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>a colorless liquid
compound (<chform>H2C:CH.CN</chform>); used as raw material for acrylic
fibers, and as a solvent.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> vinyl cyanide, cyanoethylene,
2-propenenitrile</syn>⟦br⟧
